

















































Humaniq Whitepaper

Alex Fork†

Abstract

The project of building a model of the next generation financial service
(Bank 4.0) for unbanked people. This Bank is based on Blockchain as
a platform for financial and technology start-ups. Biometric identifica-
tion instead of passports and signatures. ICO instead of shareholders.

