To put it in three words, Humaniq is banking for unbanked.
Our ultimate goals are:

ä to integrate 2.5 billion people disconnected from the international busi-
ness community,

ä to involve half of the population to cryptoeconomy.

2 What makes Humaniq special?
“The biggest room in the world is the room

for improvement.”
Helmut Schmidt

It is natural to ask why the problem of banking for unbanked cannot be
solved by Bitcoin or any other cryptocurrency. Well, indeed, what makes
Humaniq special? Did you guys make another coin whose main feature is
mobile wallet app?

